<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>The Unanchored Central Banker — Redesign Demo</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;600;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --navy: #0f1a2e;
    --navy-light: #1a2940;
    --gold: #c9a84c;
    --gold-light: #e8d5a0;
    --cream: #faf8f4;
    --warm-gray: #6b6560;
    --text: #2a2522;
    --text-light: #7a756f;
    --border: #e8e4df;
    --white: #ffffff;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
    color: var(--text);
    background: var(--white);
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  /* ===== NAV ===== */
  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(15, 26, 46, 0.95);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    padding: 0 48px;
    height: 64px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  }
  nav .logo {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    color: var(--white);
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.3px;
  }
  nav .logo span { color: var(--gold); }
  nav .nav-links { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 32px; }
  nav .nav-links a {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 400;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  nav .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--white); }
  nav .nav-links .btn-login {
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--navy);
    padding: 8px 20px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
  }
  nav .nav-links .btn-login:hover { background: var(--gold-light); }

  /* ===== HERO ===== */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: var(--navy);
    display: flex; align-items: center;
    padding: 120px 48px 80px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0;
    width: 50%; height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(201,168,76,0.08) 0%, rgba(201,168,76,0.02) 100%);
  }
  .hero-content {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
    width: 100%;
    position: relative;
  }
  .hero-text { }
  .hero-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.3);
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 56px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
  }
  .hero h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--gold);
  }
  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    max-width: 480px;
  }
  .hero-authors {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .hero-authors strong { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-weight: 500; }
  .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: center; }
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--navy);
    padding: 16px 36px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 15px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--gold-light); transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .btn-secondary {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    padding: 16px 36px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 15px;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover { color: var(--white); border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); }

  .hero-visual {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
  }
  .book-mockup {
    width: 320px;
    height: 460px;
    background: linear-gradient(145deg, #1a3a5c 0%, #0a1e35 50%, #132d4a 100%);
    border-radius: 4px 16px 16px 4px;
    box-shadow: 30px 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.5), 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.1) inset;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 40px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .book-mockup::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0;
    width: 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.3), transparent);
  }
  .book-mockup .book-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .book-mockup .book-line {
    width: 40px; height: 2px;
    background: var(--gold);
    opacity: 0.5;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .book-mockup .book-author {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ===== ENDORSEMENT STRIP ===== */
  .endorsement-strip {
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: 48px;
    text-align: center;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .endorsement-strip blockquote {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .endorsement-strip cite {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 16px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-light);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* ===== WHAT'S INSIDE ===== */
  .whats-inside {
    padding: 100px 48px;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .section-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 40px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 60px;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  }
  .chapter-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .chapter-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 32px 24px;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    display: block;
  }
  .chapter-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }
  .chapter-num {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .chapter-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: var(--navy);
  }
  .chapter-card p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ===== AUTHORS ===== */
  .authors {
    background: var(--navy);
    padding: 100px 48px;
  }
  .authors-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .authors .section-label { color: var(--gold); }
  .authors .section-title { color: var(--white); }
  .author-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
  }
  .author-card {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .author-avatar {
    width: 80px; height: 80px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--navy-light);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 2px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.3);
  }
  .author-avatar img {
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  .author-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    color: var(--white);
    font-size: 22px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .author-card .author-role {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    display: block;
  }
  .author-card p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ===== SECTION DIVIDER ===== */
  .divider {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 60px 48px 20px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }
  .divider::before, .divider::after {
    content: '———';
    color: var(--border);
    margin: 0 16px;
  }

  /* ======================================================
     MEMBERS AREA — CHAPTER NAVIGATION
     ====================================================== */
  .members-section {
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: 80px 48px 100px;
  }
  .members-header {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto 48px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .members-header h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 32px;
    color: var(--navy);
  }
  .members-nav {
    display: flex; gap: 16px;
  }
  .members-nav a {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-light);
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .members-nav a:hover, .members-nav a.active {
    background: var(--white);
    color: var(--navy);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }
  .chapter-list {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .chapter-list-item {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    cursor: pointer;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    display: block;
  }
  .chapter-list-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }
  .chapter-thumb {
    height: 180px;
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    position: relative;
  }
  .chapter-thumb::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(15,26,46,0.7) 0%, transparent 60%);
  }
  .chapter-thumb .ch-num {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 12px; left: 16px;
    color: var(--white);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .chapter-list-item .ch-body {
    padding: 20px;
  }
  .chapter-list-item h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .chapter-list-item p {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .reading-time {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 12px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* ======================================================
     CHAPTER READING VIEW
     ====================================================== */
  .reading-section {
    padding: 0;
  }
  .reading-hero {
    height: 400px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy) 0%, var(--navy-light) 100%);
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    padding: 60px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .reading-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%; right: -20%;
    width: 600px; height: 600px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(201,168,76,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .reading-hero-content { position: relative; max-width: 700px; }
  .reading-hero .ch-label {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .reading-hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    color: var(--white);
    font-size: 44px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .reading-hero .ch-meta {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  /* sticky chapter nav */
  .chapter-nav {
    position: sticky; top: 64px; z-index: 90;
    background: var(--white);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0 60px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }
  .chapter-nav a {
    padding: 16px 20px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-light);
    text-decoration: none;
    white-space: nowrap;
    border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .chapter-nav a:hover { color: var(--text); }
  .chapter-nav a.active {
    color: var(--navy);
    border-bottom-color: var(--gold);
  }

  /* reading content */
  .reading-content {
    max-width: 740px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 60px 24px 100px;
  }
  .reading-content .epigraph {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.6;
    padding: 32px 0 32px 32px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .reading-content .epigraph-cite {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-light);
    font-style: normal;
    padding-left: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }
  .reading-content p {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .reading-content h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 30px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin: 56px 0 24px;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }
  .reading-content h3 {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin: 48px 0 20px;
  }
  .reading-content .section-break {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px 0;
    color: var(--border);
    font-size: 18px;
    letter-spacing: 12px;
  }

  /* chart in reading */
  .chart-container {
    background: var(--cream);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 32px;
    margin: 40px -40px;
  }
  .chart-container .chart-label {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .chart-container img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--white);
    margin-top: 8px;
  }
  .chart-source {
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-light);
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .reading-content .section-image {
    width: calc(100% + 80px);
    margin: 48px -40px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .reading-content .section-image img {
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
  }
  .reading-content .bold-lead { font-weight: 600; }
  .reading-content .indent {
    padding-left: 32px;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .reading-content .references {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }
  .reading-content .references p {
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  /* ===== CHART CAROUSEL ===== */
  .chart-carousel {
    background: var(--cream);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 32px;
    margin: 40px -40px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .chart-carousel .carousel-track {
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }
  .chart-carousel .carousel-slides {
    display: flex;
    transition: transform 0.4s ease;
  }
  .chart-carousel .carousel-slide {
    min-width: 100%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .chart-carousel .carousel-slide .chart-label {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .chart-carousel .carousel-slide img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--white);
    margin-top: 8px;
  }
  .chart-carousel .carousel-slide .chart-source {
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-light);
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .carousel-controls {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }
  .carousel-btn {
    width: 40px; height: 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--white);
    color: var(--navy);
    font-size: 18px;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .carousel-btn:hover {
    background: var(--navy);
    color: var(--white);
    border-color: var(--navy);
  }
  .carousel-dots {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .carousel-dot {
    width: 8px; height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--border);
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .carousel-dot.active {
    background: var(--gold);
    width: 24px;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  /* ===== FOOTER ===== */
  footer {
    background: var(--navy);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    padding: 48px;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  footer a { color: var(--gold); text-decoration: none; }

  /* ===== VIEW TRANSITIONS ===== */
  .view { display: none; }
  .view.active { display: block; }

  /* Consistent chapter image style */
  .chapter-thumb {
    filter: saturate(0.6) brightness(0.85);
    transition: filter 0.3s;
  }
  .chapter-list-item:hover .chapter-thumb {
    filter: saturate(0.8) brightness(0.95);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero-content { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 40px; }
    .chapter-grid, .chapter-list { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .author-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    nav { padding: 0 24px; }
    .hero, .whats-inside, .authors, .members-section { padding-left: 24px; padding-right: 24px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="logo">The <span>Unanchored</span> Central Banker</div>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="#chapters">Chapters</a>
    <a href="#authors">Authors</a>
    <a href="#reviews">Reviews</a>
    <a href="#" class="btn-login">Read Online</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- ============================================
     VIEW 1: LANDING PAGE
     ============================================ -->
<div class="view active" id="view-landing">

<section class="hero" id="hero">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <div class="hero-tag">New Book — 2026</div>
      <h1>The <em>Unanchored</em> Central Banker</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        A book about demography, fiscal instability, and the erosion of the central bank's ability to fight inflation single-mindedly.
      </p>
      <p class="hero-authors">by <strong>Manoj Pradhan</strong> and <strong>Charles Goodhart</strong></p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#" class="btn-primary">Read Online Edition</a>
        <a href="#" class="btn-secondary">Buy Print Edition</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-visual">
      <div class="book-mockup">
        <div class="book-title">The Unanchored Central Banker</div>
        <div class="book-line"></div>
        <div class="book-author">Manoj Pradhan<br>&amp; Charles Goodhart</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ENDORSEMENT -->
<div class="endorsement-strip" id="reviews">
  <blockquote>
    "Pradhan and Goodhart succeed in highlighting the many policy challenges likely to arise from current demographic trends. Throughout, the book is remarkable for its careful assessment of competing arguments."
  </blockquote>
  <cite>— Bill White, Senior Fellow, C.D. Howe Institute; Chairman, OECD Economic &amp; Development Review Committee</cite>
</div>

<!-- WHAT'S INSIDE -->
<section class="whats-inside" id="chapters">
